description: TRUST SALE.  Unmatched Views. Turnkey Luxury.  Welcome to Unit 2732 where Trump Tower Chicago's iconic curved architecture wraps around one of the most stunning panoramas in Chicago-capturing the river, Lake Michigan, and the skyline through soaring floor-to-ceiling windows with sweeping south and east exposures.  This meticulously maintained and fully furnished 1-bedroom, 2-bath residence is designed for both luxurious living and effortless entertaining. Enjoy 10-foot ceilings, open-concept living, motorized Hunter Douglas shades, a cozy fireplace, and a spa-inspired primary bath wrapped in limestone. The chef's kitchen features sleek Snaidero Italian cabinetry and a premium Wolf, Sub-Zero, and Miele appliance suite-perfect for the culinary enthusiast.  The oversized bedroom includes a lavish ensuite, while the second full bath adds flexibility. This unit is move-in ready and offers the option to participate in the Trump Hotel rental program for those seeking an income-generating pied-a-terre or investment opportunity. As a resident, you'll enjoy full access to world-class 5-star amenities, including: White-glove concierge and 24-hour front desk; 23,000 sq ft wellness center with an indoor pool, fitness studio, steam rooms, and a luxury spa; Award-winning dining at Terrace 16 and Rebar; valet, room service, business center, dog park, and more. Set in the heart of River North, just steps from the Riverwalk, Michigan Avenue, the Magnificent Mile, and world-class shopping, dining, and entertainment. Designed by Adrian Smith of SOM (architect of the Burj Khalifa), this is not just a home-it's a front-row seat to the best of Chicago. Quite simply, it's the best view in the building-and the city. There are specific terms of sale, please contact the listing agent
